  "detailed_description": "Explore, fight, and platform through deadly plants and obstacles as a potato named Tater Spud. Interact with friendly flora and fauna to begin to learn what is causing the world to turn rotten.<br><br>Play as Tater Spud to gain powerful abilities and use collectables to upgrade your gear with the goal of defeating some of the nastiest plant-animals ever seen. Whether day or night there will be dangers to overcome (or die a lot from). <br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Hidden Powerups<br></li><li> Collectable Tater Tots and Mushrooms<br></li><li> Upgradeable Weapons<br></li><li> Tough Bosses<br></li><li> Talking Plants & Animals (woah)<br></li><li> Free Updates</li></ul><br><u>Tater Spud (left) and Murphy Mango (right)</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064000/extras/c24e7ade30fa9d75ee5432d39b770d50.poster.avif?t=1672765698\" width=460 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064000/extras/c24e7ade30fa9d75ee5432d39b770d50.webm?t=1672765698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064000/extras/c24e7ade30fa9d75ee5432d39b770d50.mp4?t=1672765698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Explore, fight, and platform through deadly plants and obstacles as a potato named Tater Spud. Interact with friendly flora and fauna to begin to learn what is causing the world to turn rotten.<br><br>Play as Tater Spud to gain powerful abilities and use collectables to upgrade your gear with the goal of defeating some of the nastiest plant-animals ever seen. Whether day or night there will be dangers to overcome (or die a lot from). <br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Hidden Powerups<br></li><li> Collectable Tater Tots and Mushrooms<br></li><li> Upgradeable Weapons<br></li><li> Tough Bosses<br></li><li> Talking Plants & Animals (woah)<br></li><li> Free Updates</li></ul><br><u>Tater Spud (left) and Murphy Mango (right)</u><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064000/extras/c24e7ade30fa9d75ee5432d39b770d50.poster.avif?t=1672765698\" width=460 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064000/extras/c24e7ade30fa9d75ee5432d39b770d50.webm?t=1672765698\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2064000/extras/c24e7ade30fa9d75ee5432d39b770d50.mp4?t=1672765698\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
